   169→		projectName:       "My Project",
   170→	}
   171→
   172→	// sendProjectNotifications calls defaultSenders() which creates real HTTP
   173→	// senders. To test without making HTTP calls, we test that the store
   174→	// methods are called correctly. The real HTTP send will fail (no server),
   175→	// but that is logged and not returned as an error.
   176→	//
   177→	// To properly unit test the send path, we verify that
